T1  - UNEQUAL PEACE
AU  - Kamranzadeh, Ali
AU  - Zheng, Charles Z.
Y1  - 2025/02/01
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12725
T2  - International Economic Review
