T1  - THE UNPRECEDENTED FALL IN U.S. REVOLVING CREDIT
AU  - Raveendranathan, Gajendran
AU  - Stefanidis, Georgios
Y1  - 2025/02/01
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12727
